        " صَلَّى اَللَّهُ عَلَيْهِ وَ آلِهِ: «صَدَقَةُ اَلسِّرِّ تُطْفِئُ غَضَبَ اَلرَّبِّ جَلَّ جَلاَلُهُ »."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.bab-ul-qaim-publications": [
          "Hadith.1735 - The Prophet (sw), peace and blessings be upon him and his family, said:\n\"Charity given in secret extinguishes the wrath of the Lord (azj), majestic and exalted is He.\""
